name: Freedomhealthonline
overview:
Freedomhealthonline is a UK Online Doctor Service based at 60 Harley Street London W1G 7HA. Freedomhealthonline is a subsidiary of Freedomhealth and is a fully Care Quality Commission registered private health care clinic.

Freedomhealthonline provides a range of Online Medical consultations and services. Consultations are assessed by UK GMC registered physicians who operate from 60 Harley Street London W1G 7HA. Medications are issued from UK pharmacies.

Freedomhealthonline provides online consultations for assessment of the following conditions:- Morning After Pill assessment and treatment; Erectile Dysfunction assessment and treatment; Malaria Prophylaxis tablets; Contraceptive tablets; Male Pattern Baldness and Hair Loss treatments.
